The paper discusses statistical machine learning techniques such as supervised and unsupervised learning, deep learning, online learning, and Gaussian processes. These techniques are commonly used in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), statistics (cs.ST), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
